[Event "Psychopathy in Chess - Luzhin Defence.: Solution 1"]
[Date "2020.11.03"]
[Result "*"]
[Variant "Standard"]
[ECO "?"]
[Opening "?"]
[StudyName "Psychopathy in Chess - Luzhin Defence."]
[ChapterName "Solution 1"]
[ChapterURL "https://lichess.org/study/iEq8b4xO/kEVnXBGN"]
[Annotator "https://lichess.org/@/Tasshaq"]
[FEN "1BB4B/1Bppppp1/B1pbbkpn/N1pbbbp1/2pbpbp1/2p1p1p1/2P1P1P1/1B5K w - - 0 1"]
[SetUp "1"]
[UTCDate "2020.11.03"]
[UTCTime "14:06:14"]

{ Black cannot do anything other than wait its end. Once the king gets to f8, the weakness on g7 will be decisive. But king has to travel a long long road like in monopoly game to help the bishop in the corner. } { [%csl Gg7][%cal Gh1a1,Ga1a8,Ga8f8] }
1. Kg1 Ng8 2. Kf1 Nh6 3. Ke1 Ng8 4. Kd1 Nh6 5. Kc1 Ng8 6. Ba2 Nh6 7. Kb1 Ng8 8. Ka1 { King has reached 1st checkpoint. } { [%csl Ga1] } 8... Nh6 9. Bb1 Ng8 10. Ka2 Nh6 11. Ka3 Ng8 12. Ka4 { Excuse me Sir, can you please move aside? } 12... Nh6 13. Ba8 Ng8 14. Nb7 { Sure. } 14... Nh6 15. Ka5 { Excuse me. } 15... Ng8 16. Nd8 Nh6 17. B6b7 Ng8 18. Ka6 Nh6 19. Ka7 Ng8 20. Ba6 Nh6 21. Nb7 Ng8 22. Na5 Nh6 23. Ba8b7 (23. Kb7 Ng8 24. Ba7 Nh6 25. Kb8 Ng8 26. Bcb7 Nh6 27. Kc8 Ng8 28. Kd8 Nh6 29. Ke8 Ng8 30. Kf8 Nh6 31. Bxg7#) 23... Ng8 24. Ka8 { King has reached the 2nd checkpoint. } { [%csl Ga8] } 24... Nh6 25. Ba7 Ng8 26. Kb8 Nh6 27. Ba8 Ng8 28. Bcb7 Nh6 { Oh, here i go. } 29. Kc8 Ng8 30. Kd8 Nh6 31. Ke8 { Almost there. } 31... Ng8 32. Kf8 { Uh, finally. Am i late? } 32... Nh6 33. Bxg7# *


