{ In this study, i ll pick some of the original tactics that appeared in my 960 games and which that are highly unusual motifs. Study called Tasshaqs Fav Games consists mainly games against Titled players or strong opponents and instructive games.

However, main Theme in this study is not the game as a whole, but some unusual moments and original tactics, regardless of the game quality and opponent strength. Also there will be some honorary mentions of tactical motifs, that are instructive or interesting in some way. }
 *


