[SetUp "1"]
[UTCDate "2020.07.02"]
[UTCTime "08:49:07"]

1. Nb3 Ng6 { This game i played very quickly without calculation, almost all of my moves were either premove or were played in 1-3 seconds. An attack based on feeling. } 2. c3 e5 { one important thing to consider here is that both sides are likely to castle 0-0-0 so it makes sense that all pieces gravitate towards the that side of the board. } 3. Bc2 f6 4. O-O-O d5 5. d4 Nb6 6. f3 Nc4 7. e4 Be7 8. exd5 Qa4 9. Kb1 Bxd5 10. dxe5 O-O-O 11. exf6 Rxf6 { [%cal Gf6a6] } 12. Bd4 Ra6 13. Nc1 Qb5 14. Bb3 Nxb2 15. Kxb2 Ba3+ 16. Kc2 Bxc1 17. Rxc1 (17. Bxd5 { if he took, there would be a nice mate } 17... Qb2+ 18. Kd3 Nf4+ 19. Ke4 Qb1+ 20. Ke5 Rxd5#) 17... Bxb3+ 18. axb3 Ra2+ { White resigned in view of mate in 2. } { [%cal Gc2d1,Gb5d3,Gc2b1,Gb5b3] } 0-1


