{ How to continue the attack? White has improved his position to its fullest and now it is time for execution. }
1. Kh1! { Now white wants to make use of g file as well as rerouting bishop to h5. Defending e6, f6 and various threats on g-file with rook and Ng5+ Ne5+ ideas will be impossible for black. } { [%csl Ge6,Gf6,Gg6,Gh8][%cal Gg1g8] } 1... a5 2. g4 fxg4 3. Bxg4 { [%csl Ge6,Gf6][%cal Gg4h5,Gg4e6] } 3... f5 4. Bh5 Ref8 5. Bxf7 Qxf7 6. Rg1 { [%csl Gg6][%cal Gf4g6] } 6... Rg8 7. Reg2 Rxg2 8. Rxg2 { [%csl Gg6] } 8... Nde8 9. Ng6+ Kg7 10. Ne5+ { 1-0 Black resigns. } 1-0


