{ White has all the advantage. Material and position. Now it is time to finish, but how to convert? }
22. e5!! { Breakthrough into blacks camp. Black cannot regroup his pieces and white also has a material advantage. Advantage of material advantage is that 1) you can give a piece back when needed for a bigger advantage 2) Outnumbering. you have simply more pieces to attack than opponent can defend with. } { [%csl Gb6,Gb8,Ge1,Gd2,Gd3,Gf3,Gg8] } 22... dxe5 23. Nxe5! { [%csl Gc6,Ge7] } 23... fxe5 24. Qxg5+ Kf7 25. Qxe5 Nbd7 26. Qxe7+ Kg8 27. Qg5+ Kh8 28. Re7 { 1-0 Black resigns. } { [%csl Gg7] } 1-0


