th move, i saced knight and got it back on e3 later. But actually, when i sacrificed knight, i captured a pawn, which was a potential queen, so i kinda eliminated a queen, which then played a role when i for example promoted on c line i ended up being queen up simply. } { [%csl Gd6] [%clk 0:00:08] } 29. h8=Q { [%clk 0:00:09] } 29... Qd6# { 0-1 Black wins by checkmate. } { [%clk 0:00:07] } 0-1


