 to see with 30 sec left. } { [%csl Gh2][%cal Gb8h2,Gh3h1] [%clk 0:00:46] } 23. Bxe5 { [%clk 0:00:11] } (23. Qd6 h2 24. Bc7 { [%csl Gd8] } 24... Ne6 25. Qxc6+ Ke7 26. Qd6+ Ke8 27. Qc6+ Kf8 (27... Ke7 28. Qd6+ Ke8 29. Qc6+ { black has to settle for draw. }) 28. Bd6+ Kg8 29. Qe8+ { [%cal Gg8h7,Ge8f7] } 29... Kg7 { [%cal Gd6e5] }) 23... Bxe5 { [%clk 0:00:44] } 24. dxe5 { [%clk 0:00:12] } 24... h2 { [%clk 0:00:44] } 25. Nd2 { [%clk 0:00:12] } 25... h1=Q { [%clk 0:00:43] } 26. Qc3 { [%clk 0:00:12] } 26... Ne6 { [%clk 0:00:28] } 27. Qxc6+ { [%clk 0:00:09] } 27... Kf8 { [%clk 0:00:29] } 28. Qd6+ { [%clk 0:00:09] } 28... Kg7 { [%clk 0:00:27] } 29. Nxf3 { [%clk 0:00:05] } 29... Qxf3+ { [%clk 0:00:27] } 30. Kd2 { [%clk 0:00:05] } 30... Qxf2+ { [%clk 0:00:26] } 31. Kc3 { [%clk 0:00:06] } 31... e3 { [%clk 0:00:23] } 32. Qe7 { [%clk 0:00:06] } 32... e2 { 0-1 White resigns. } { [%clk 0:00:22] } 0-1


