1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 c5 3. Nf3?! { Inaccuracy. d5 was best. } (3. d5 b5 4. cxb5 a6 5. bxa6 e6 6. dxe6 fxe6 7. e3 d5) 3... cxd4 4. Nxd4 e6 5. g3 Nc6 6. Bg2 Bc5 7. Nb3 Be7 8. Nc3 O-O 9. O-O d6 10. Bf4 Nh5 11. e3 Nxf4 12. exf4 Bd7 13. Qd2 Qb8 14. Rfe1 g6?! { Inaccuracy. a5 was best. } (14... a5 15. a4) 15. h4 a6 16. h5?! { Inaccuracy. Rad1 was best. } (16. Rad1) 16... b5?! { Inaccuracy. Rc8 was best. } (16... Rc8 17. h6 b5 18. Nd5 exd5 19. cxd5 Bf8 20. dxc6 Bxc6 21. Bh3 Rc7 22. Nd4 Bb7 23. f5) 17. hxg6 hxg6 18. Nc5 dxc5? { Mistake. Qc7 was best. } (18... Qc7 19. Nxd7 Qxd7 20. cxb5 axb5 21. Nxb5 d5 22. Rec1 Rfc8 23. Bf1 Bb4 24. Qd1 Bf8 25. a4) 19. Qxd7 Rc8 20. Rxe6 Ra7 21. Rxg6+ fxg6 22. Qe6+ Kg7 23. Bxc6 Rd8?! { Inaccuracy. Rf8 was best. } (23... Rf8 24. cxb5) 24. cxb5 Bf6? { Mistake. Rd6 was best. } (24... Rd6 25. Qe4 Bf6 26. Qf3 Qb6 27. Ne4 Rxc6 28. bxc6 Qxc6 29. Kg2 Bxb2 30. Rh1 Re7 31. Rh7+) 25. Ne4 Bd4 26. bxa6 Qb6 27. Rd1 Qxa6?? { Blunder. Rf8 was best. } (27... Rf8 28. b4) 28. Rxd4 Rxd4 29. Qf6+ Kg8 30. Qxg6+ Kf8 31. Qe8+ Kg7 32. Qe5+ Kg8 33. Nf6+?! { Inaccuracy. Qg5+ was best. } (33. Qg5+ Rg7 34. Bd5+ Rxd5 35. Qxd5+ Kh7 36. Qh5+ Kg8 37. Qe8+ Kh7 38. f5 Qh6 39. f6 Qg6) 33... Kf7 34. Be8+ Kf8 35. Qxc5+ Qd6 36. Qxa7 Qxf6 37. Bh5 Rd2 38. b3?! { Inaccuracy. a4 was best. } (38. a4 Qe7) 38... Rb2? { Mistake. Qe7 was best. } (38... Qe7 39. Qb6 Rxa2 40. Qd4 Qa7 41. Qh8+ Ke7 42. Qe8+ Kd6 43. Qe5+ Kd7 44. Be2 Qc7 45. Bg4+) 39. Kg2 { 1-0 Black resigns. } 1-0


